SUMMARY:PBI Dataviz World Champs - Meet the finalists
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nEver wondered what separates great 
 data visualization from world‑class? This is your chance to find out\, s
 traight from the best in the world.\n\nJoin us for an exclusive session wi
 th the four finalists heading to FabCon on March 18th\, where they’ll ba
 ttle it out for the title of 2026 Power BI DataViz World Champion. Before 
 they step onto the global stage\, you’ll get an inside look at how these
  elite designers think\, create\, and win.\n\nThe finalists will walk thro
 ugh their preliminary‑round winning reports\, unpack their design decisi
 ons\, and share the creative and analytical processes behind their standou
 t work. Expect real‑world insights\, practical tips you can immediately 
 apply\, and four distinct perspectives on what exceptional Power BI design
  really looks like.\n\nCome ready to learn\, get inspired\, and see what
 ’s possible when data visualization is pushed to its limits.\n\nCheck ou
 t their reports at https://aka.ms/pbidvwc26/finalists
