SUMMARY:Maximize the Cost Efficiency of AI Agents on Azure
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nAs organizations accelerate their a
 doption of AI agents\, the need to balance innovation with financial disci
 pline has never been more critical. In this Reactor session\, you'll learn
  how to make cost conscious\, strategic decisions that maximize the ROI of
  your AI agent investments across their entire lifecycle.\n\n***\n\n**Reso
 urces**\n\n* [Learn More here](https://aka.ms/maximize-cost-efficiency-ai-
 agents)
